    <h1>Google Medic Update</h1>
    <p class="description">A broad core algorithm update launched August 1, 2018 that hit health and financial (YMYL) websites lacking credentialed authors and E-E-A-T signals — with some sites losing <strong>40-70% of organic traffic</strong> overnight.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
