              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The Medic Update rewarded sites with detailed author bios listing real credentials, links to professional profiles, citations to primary research, clear editorial policies, medical or financial expert review processes, and comprehensive About Us pages demonstrating organizational legitimacy.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

